Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates really are going\Nto come, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're definitely gonna show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone thinks it's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this village!\NI want to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Klahadore's\Npirates we're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm scared!\NWhat's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we'd risk our lives\Nbecause of sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Clash with the Black Cat Pirates!\NGreat Battle on the Slope!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. They're going to attack\Nfrom this shore at daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only route into\Nthe village is this one slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything else is cliff,\Nmaking it tougher to come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if we can\Ndefend this slope to the death,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the village won't get attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about it is, but the\Nrest depends on our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you guys do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cut.\N--Stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Steal.\N--I can hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Klahadore-san! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How is she?\N--She's resting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed quite exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think such a thing happened\Nwhile I was at the next town over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Usopp lad certainly\Nknows how to cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of all things,\Nhe claimed you were a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a transparent lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that seems to be a\Npresent from her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your third year at this mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's a sort of commemoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commemoration...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your current glasses seem to slip often,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she custom-ordered those!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a nice, thoughtful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A commemoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, tomorrow is a\Nday to commemorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crescent moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nights like this make my heart race,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my blood stir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Klahadore-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to her present?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be accepting a present, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be this--\Nit'll be this entire mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no more need\Nto continue the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident is going to occur\Nin a few hours, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly been three long years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost daybreak!\NPlease wake up, Captain Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good morning, Captain!\N--Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My policy is to say "good morning"\Nwith the morning sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He seems to be in a bad mood.\N--He did just wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look! The moon's still up,\Nand it's the middle of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you shout loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our apologies, sir! We're sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, fellows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning? That's the\Nopposite of what he just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! He's in a better\Nmood now, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit bein' confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they won't be able\Nto climb up this slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to all this oil\Nwe've laid out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let 'em slip and\Nslide on this slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then beat the crap out of\N'em while they flail about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what,\Nwe will protect this slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, let's just hope\Nthat none of us slip down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be like diving right\Ninto an ant-lion pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can\Nthink up stuff this cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to\Ncheekiness and slingshots,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm utterly confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, men! Go ashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash the village\Nand head for the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! There are\Ntwo strange boats here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I check them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave 'em. They're not treasure ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw up our schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's all bright now.\NWhat's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they overslept or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll definitely show up. Lot's of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just my imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hear, "Yaaah!"\Ncoming from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I definitely hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place just like\Nthis to the north, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this is the wrong shore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where they had\Ntheir secret meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I just assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna get into the\Nvillage! Where is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run straight north from here,\Nyou'll get there in three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terrain there is\Nalmost exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we just need to\Nstop them at the slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We'll do it somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The north shore is where our boats are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna take the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there in 20 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! My brilliant Oil\NStrategy was all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My treasure...\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! We have to hurry--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let go, you moron!\N--Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! The treasure's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to get back up somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to let them enter the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy sure runs fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight north!\NStraight north! Straight north!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in big trouble\Nif they touch my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone at the top of the hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm completely ready to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back now, if you don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--? I'm the first one here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was running way ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?! I can't climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the village now! That's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said north, so I ran\Nin a cold-ish direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that boy who\Noverheard our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm warning you!\NTurn back now while you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else my 100 million crewmen will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beat the crap out of you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! That's even\Nworse than a kid's lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 100 million?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's obviously lying, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so naïve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! They saw through it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seriously thought\Nhe could fool us, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Jango! Shocking news!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?! That's bad!\N--No! It's not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found treasure\Nin those weird boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An incredible amount!\NMaybe 4, no, 5 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Five million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there that much\Nmoney in those guys' boats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But you can have it!\N--What?! You'll give us the treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for that treasure,\NI ask that you turn back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! You think you can\Nbuy us off with money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disgraceful guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool. We're pirates, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're obviously going\Nto take this treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good enough of\Na reason for us to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! On "one, two,\NJango," you'll let us by!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that weapon from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit saying stupid crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who's she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! This is no time to\Nhypnotize yourself and let people by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boat's treasure is mine!\NI won't let you have a single Berry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to it!\NI'll come take it back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could\Ngive them my treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with just\Nsaying they can have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!\NAfter I just saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--I forgot to mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't watch his ring\Nall the way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hypnotist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hypnosis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Where's Luffy?\NHe ran here first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno! He either\Nchickened out or got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got lost, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Just when we need him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take command here.\NGo kick their butts! I'll cover you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Hold on, why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can take on that\Nhuge army! I'm weak, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me\Njust 'cause I'm a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared my legs are\Nshaking like crazy! See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, look! I'm so scared\NI have tears in my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are bone dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna lie,\Nlie more realistically!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to mess with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush 'em and head\Nfor the village, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I have caltrops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You do have some good stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme, gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caltrop Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Nami!\NShe's gonna pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Which way is the north shore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight north!\NStraight north! Straight north!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is north?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Special Attack: Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go! Keep it up, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna quit fighting for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even fought yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are caltrops behind us too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! You dropped 'em there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the damn way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously think you can stop us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys! Captain Kuro is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, you bastard! Let the hell go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Take this! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let you get past this slope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I only lied, like I always do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the village is going to have\Njust another ordinary day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I absolutely won't let you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kid! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit bothering with them\Nand get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that\Nthis is Captain Kuro's plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens\Nto throw his plan off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll kill every one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that,\Nyou dumbasses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hey, now...\N--Yeah, hurry to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Don't go to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please!\NPlease don't kill everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this village! I want to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this, Captain Jango?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody mentioned guys\Nlike them were in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those\Nunchallenging guys just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!\NI'm not satisfied, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! How dare you\Nkick me down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say which way was north!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all know full well what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to those who upset my plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think they can\Ntake their sweet time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they've already forgotten that fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll slaughter them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Klahadore from the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he walking toward the shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this early in the morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this the place?!\N--Damn you, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.78,0:24:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you leave me down there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.44,0:24:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Zoro's really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to pay, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Get sleepy at the\Ncount of "one, two, Jango"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Quit sleeping, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look at that guy's hand!\N--Don't avoid the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.99,0:24:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.49,0:24:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Terrifying Duo!\NMeowban Brothers vs. Zoro"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.66,0:24:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
